About
-----
This is a demo web app which compares poker hands with each other and rank them to detect the winner hand.


How to run
----------
1. Build project with maven (e.g. mvn clean package)

2. Execute jar file under target folder.
   java -jar target/*.jar

   If you have a port conflict add --server.port=<desired_port> parameter on above command.


How to use
----------
1. Open a browser and visit http://localhost:8080/index.html
2. Add at least two poker hands by clicking '+ Add Poker Hand' button.
3. Pick up cards for each hand. Be sure every card is used only once.
4. Finally click to 'Compare Poker Hands' button to see results.


Credits
-------
Poker card images taken from https://code.google.com/p/vector-playing-cards/. 
See this http://byronknoll.blogspot.de/2011/03/vector-playing-cards.html blog entry for more details.
